description:
Data associated with Chen, Nieman, Spurrell et al "Human lung cancer harbors spatially-organized stem-immunity hubs that associate with response to immunotherapy" Nature Immunology, 2024.&nbsp; 
 (1) Multiplex RNA scope. Processed cell-level data from 3 datasets, separated into manually selected "Stem Immunity" regions and "Tumor" regions, in separate files.&nbsp; 
 (2) GeoMx. Unprocessed GeoMex data, with standard fields provided by Nanostring software.&nbsp; 
 (3) MERFISH. Transcript-level information, including CellPose and Baysor segmentation.&nbsp; 
 (4) Co-registered multispectral RNA and protein images. Processed cell-level data from 46 patients. Patient-level meta data information is available in supplementary table 1, tab B_Patient_Metadata. Fluorophore channel information is Figure 1a.&nbsp; 
 Paper:&nbsp; https://www.nature.com/articles/s41590-024-01792-2

